#: .\ab_gunmods_override.json
msgid "beam scatterer"
msgid_plural "beam scatterers"
msgstr[0] "光束散射器"

#: .\ab_gunmods_override.json
msgid ""
"A set of optics made to fit on laser weapons, which will diffract the laser "
"beam into several lower powered beams.  This increases point-blank damage, "
"but reduces range."
msgstr "一套專為激光武器設計的光學組件，可將激光束衍射成數道威力較低的射線。這提升了近身傷害，但降低了射程。"

#: .\ab_gunmods_override.json
msgid "heat ray conversion"
msgid_plural "heat ray conversions"
msgstr[0] "熱射線轉換器"

#: .\ab_gunmods_override.json
msgid ""
"A rare advanced electronics unit that converts a laser weapon into a "
"incendiary heat weapon, at the cost of a decreased damage output and "
"increased power consumption."
msgstr "一種罕見的先進電子單元，可將激光武器轉換為燃燒性熱能武器，代價是降低傷害輸出並增加能耗。"

#: .\ab_gunmods_override.json
msgid "lens"
msgstr "透鏡"

#: .\ab_gunmods_override.json
msgid "Type-39 auxiliary laser"
msgid_plural "Type-39 auxiliary lasers"
msgstr[0] "39型輔助激光器"

#: .\ab_gunmods_override.json
msgid ""
"The Pan Pacific Consortium Type-39 Laser Auxiliary Weapon System is designed"
" to can be mounted under the barrel of military rifles, allowing continued "
"fighting even when the main weapon's ammunition is exhausted."
msgstr "泛太平洋聯合體39型激光輔助武器系統設計用於安裝在軍用步槍槍管下方，即使主武器彈藥耗盡也能繼續作戰。"

#: .\ab_gunmods_override.json
msgid "underbarrel"
msgstr "下掛式"

#: .\ab_gunmods_override.json
msgid "focusing unit"
msgid_plural "focusing units"
msgstr[0] "聚焦單元"

#: .\ab_gunmods_override.json
msgid ""
"A set of optics made to fit laser weapons, which will focus the laser beam "
"into a thin high powered beam.  This increases range, but reduces pure "
"damage."
msgstr "一套專為激光武器設計的光學組件，可將激光束聚焦成一道纖細的高能射線。這提升了射程，但降低了純粹傷害。"

#: .\ab_gunmods_override.json
msgid "optimized capacitor"
msgid_plural "optimized capacitors"
msgstr[0] "優化電容器"

#: .\ab_gunmods_override.json
msgid ""
"A finely tuned optimized capacitor unit. It significantly reduces power "
"consumption of laser weapons in exchange for damage."
msgstr "一個經過精細調校的優化電容器單元。它顯著降低了激光武器的能耗，但以犧牲傷害為代價。"

#: .\ab_gunmods_override.json
msgid "emitter"
msgstr "發射器"

#: .\ab_gunmods_override.json
msgid "high density capacitor"
msgid_plural "high density capacitors"
msgstr[0] "高密度電容器"

#: .\ab_gunmods_override.json
msgid ""
"A capacitor with a higher energy density increases range and damage; at the "
"cost of a increased power consumption."
msgstr "一種能量密度更高的電容器，可增加射程和傷害；代價是功耗增加。"

#: .\ab_weapons.json
msgid "Type-38 laser pistol"
msgid_plural "Type-38 laser pistols"
msgstr[0] "38型激光手槍"

#: .\ab_weapons.json
msgid ""
"The service sidearm of the Pan Pacific Coalition, the Type-38 is relatively "
"light and nimble laser pistol."
msgstr "38型是泛太平洋聯盟的制式手槍，是一種相對輕巧靈活的激光手槍。"

#: .\ab_weapons.json
msgid "Type-40 laser carbine"
msgid_plural "Type-40 laser carbines"
msgstr[0] "40型激光卡賓槍"

#: .\ab_weapons.json
msgid ""
"A lightweight laser weapon developed by the Pan Pacific Consortium. This "
"carbine compensates for its lack of firepower with rapid fire rate."
msgstr "由泛太平洋聯盟開發的輕型激光武器。這款卡賓槍以高射速彌補了火力不足。"

#: .\ab_weapons.json
msgid "semi-auto"
msgstr "半自動"

#: .\ab_weapons.json
msgid "3 rd."
msgstr "3 發"

#: .\ab_weapons.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "smg"
msgstr "衝鋒槍"

#: .\ab_weapons.json
msgid "Type-41 laser precision rifle"
msgid_plural "Type-41 laser precision rifles"
msgstr[0] "41型激光精確步槍"

#: .\ab_weapons.json
msgid ""
"A precise, powerful laser weapon with a huge energy consumption. The Pan "
"Pacific Consortium designed this weapon for designated marksmen."
msgstr "一種精準、強大的激光武器，能耗巨大。泛太平洋聯盟為指定射手設計了這款武器。"

#: .\ab_weapons.json
msgid "Type-37 scatter laser"
msgid_plural "Type-37 scatter lasers"
msgstr[0] "37型散射激光槍"

#: .\ab_weapons.json
msgid ""
"A close-quarter laser weapon developed by the Pan Pacific Consortium. In the"
" early days of laser weapon development, the PPC's engineers came up with "
"the idea of solving the low accuracy of their laser weapons by fastening "
"several barrels together."
msgstr "泛太平洋聯盟開發的近戰激光武器。在激光武器發展的早期，PPC的工程師提出了通過將多個槍管固定在一起來解決激光武器精度低下的想法。"

#: .\ab_weapons.json
msgid "multi"
msgstr "多重"

#: .\ab_weapons.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "shotgun"
msgstr "霰彈槍"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Arsenal Breach"
msgstr "軍火庫突破"

#. ~ Description for Arsenal Breach
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Adds futuristic weapons"
msgstr "添加未來主義武器"
